01:03:10.960 --> 01:03:12.160
and here's why.

01:03:13.200 --> 01:03:15.200
The problem with this change is

01:03:15.840 --> 01:03:18.400
the Connecticut general state statute

01:03:18.560 --> 01:03:21.120
10 dash two twenty

01:03:20.485 --> 01:03:22.565
requires that the board of education,

01:03:23.205 --> 01:03:28.085
quote, shall have charge of the schools of its respective school district,

01:03:28.565 --> 01:03:32.165
shall make a continuing study of the need for school facilities

01:03:32.980 --> 01:03:35.700
and of a long term school building program,

01:03:36.820 --> 01:03:40.820
and shall have the care and maintenance and operation of buildings,

01:03:41.540 --> 01:03:42.340
lands,

01:03:42.820 --> 01:03:43.940
apparatus,

01:03:44.420 --> 01:03:45.620
and other property

01:03:45.700 --> 01:03:47.220
used for school purposes,

01:03:47.915 --> 01:03:48.715
unquote.

01:03:49.675 --> 01:03:52.795
This requires that school property is kept separate

01:03:52.875 --> 01:03:54.235
from other town

01:03:55.355 --> 01:03:56.715
owned property.

01:03:57.915 --> 01:04:02.075
Hence, the need for including the schools as a separate special permit use.

01:04:03.120 --> 01:04:04.720
General state statutes

01:04:05.120 --> 01:04:07.280
supersede all local action.

01:04:08.400 --> 01:04:12.000
Another concern with the removal of the school identifier

01:04:12.000 --> 01:04:14.080
and lumping it in with the municipal

01:04:14.480 --> 01:04:17.200
is that while the school is a municipal building,

01:04:18.075 --> 01:04:20.715
that does not mean it's public access

01:04:21.115 --> 01:04:24.235
as would be expected in other municipal buildings

01:04:24.555 --> 01:04:27.595
as included in the proposed definition.

01:04:28.635 --> 01:04:34.380
Today, there is great need for safety and security of the school building and property.

01:04:35.340 --> 01:04:38.060
Hence, the need for including schools

01:04:38.140 --> 01:04:41.660
as a separate special permit used once again.

01:04:42.220 --> 01:04:44.700
As we have seen with other laws,

01:04:45.340 --> 01:04:47.740
some examples include when masking

01:04:48.155 --> 01:04:49.675
mandates for issue

01:04:49.915 --> 01:04:51.995
with laws pertaining to smoking,

01:04:52.395 --> 01:04:54.955
carrying of weapons, other legislation.

01:04:55.435 --> 01:04:58.475
There's often a diff difference between school

01:04:58.715 --> 01:04:59.995
and municipal buildings.

01:05:01.690 --> 01:05:05.530
As the Connecticut general statute requires the board of ed to

01:05:05.770 --> 01:05:08.170
have charge of the buildings and the lands,

01:05:08.650 --> 01:05:12.250
there is a definite requirement for a separate identifier

01:05:12.330 --> 01:05:14.410
to be in the special permit usage.

01:05:15.885 --> 01:05:17.885
As the Andover Board of Education,

01:05:18.285 --> 01:05:20.605
we must insist that the identifier

01:05:20.605 --> 01:05:21.645
of schools

01:05:22.045 --> 01:05:29.005
remains in the list of special permit zoning uses in addition to the words municipal land uses

01:05:29.165 --> 01:05:30.685
in the revised regulation.

